General.Name: Atlan Holdings Bhd
General.Description: Atlan Holdings Bhd, an investment holding company, engages in the trading of duty-free goods, and dutiable and non-dutiable merchandise in Malaysia. The company operates through Property and Hospitality; Trading of Duty Free Goods, Dutiable and Non-Dutiable Merchandise; and Automotive segments. It is involved in the wholesale and retail of duty-free and non-dutiable merchandise, including imported duty free beverages, tobacco products, chocolates, confectionery, perfumery, cosmetics, and souvenirs; and manufacture and distribution of metallic tubes, fuel filter neck, fuel tanks modules, metal stamping parts, plastic and metal fuel tanks, screw jacks, and tubings, as well as sub-assembly of instrument panels. The company also engages in the general construction and apartment hotel business; investment, development, and management of properties; development of resorts; and cultivation of oil palm. In addition, it distributes, wholesales, and retails beverages; and manufactures and markets exhaust systems and wheelbarrows, as well as provides management, financial, technical, and other ancillary services. The company was incorporated in 1988 and is based in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia.
